---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🌿 Greetings from Asturias!</h1>
			<p>
				Hello! I live and work in <strong>Asturias</strong>, a breathtaking region in Northern Spain known as the "Natural Paradise." 
				After spending time here, I’ve realized that its emerald mountains, rugged coastlines, and 
				incredible culture are too good not to share.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am officially inviting you to visit this wonderful place. Whether you are a nature lover, 
				a foodie looking for the best cider and cheese, or just someone seeking a peaceful escape, 
				Asturias has it all.
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Why visit?</strong> Here is what I can show you and tell you about:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>The majestic peaks of <strong>Picos de Europa</strong>.</li>
				<li>Hidden beaches with crystal clear water along the Cantabrian Sea.</li>
				<li>The secrets of traditional cider pouring and local <em>espichas</em>.</li>
				<li>Charming coastal towns like Llanes, Cudillero, and Luarca.</li>
				<li>The rich history and pre-Romanesque architecture of Oviedo and Gijón.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Don't just take my word for it — come and see for yourself! I’ll be your local guide, 
				showing you the hidden gems that only people living here know about. 
				I'll make sure you experience the true heart of the Asturias.
			</p>
			<p>
				Feel free to reach out if you're planning a trip or just want to ask a question 
				about life here in the north of Spain. See you soon!
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
